# Added checking for blank option to MODEM option processing.
#
# Revision 1.9  1998/08/14 01:11:29  jws
# Author: jws@y6maint1 (John Soisson)
# Added reading of FDDI and MODEM options from WSPCS.cfg.
# Cleaned up FDDI initialization section so that the previous
# version of fddi.out is saved and FDDI initialization is
# performed only if the option is set.  Added automatic dialing
# of modem if the MODEM option is set.
#
# Revision 1.8  1998/07/31 15:31:19  jws
# Author: jws@y6maint1 (John Soisson)
# Added commands to build the shopping list files only if the
# shopping list file is older than the corresponding Tdoc file.
#
# Revision 1.7  1998/07/23 18:35:45  jws
# Author: jws@y6maint1 (John Soisson)
# Added statements to support automatic workstation restart.
#
# Revision 1.6  1998/06/23 18:16:34  jws
# Author: jws@y6maint1 (John Soisson)
# added initialization of FDDI input file "fddi.in".
#
# Revision 1.5  1998/06/17 18:28:58  jws
# Author: jws@y6maint1 (John Soisson)
# Changed to use sysLog instead of tee to log
# WSPCS output to circular log.
#
# Revision 1.4  1997/12/03 18:22:05  leo
